      "content": "wait, you just said in the first message that they SHOULD be allowed to opt out to respect diversity, but now you're saying it's \"clear\" they're undermining society and that the \"right approach\" is to just follow secular laws. how can both be true? aren't you just saying that religious freedom only matters until it gets in the way of what the government wants?",
